\"from\": 227, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"snow\", \"from\": 237, \"to\": 241}, {\"ngram\": \"100%\", \"from\": 242, \"to\": 246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"1 to 3 inches of snow expected.\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 279, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"1 to 3 inches\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 261}, {\"ngram\": \"snow\", \"from\": 265, \"to\": 269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Updated: December 2, 2025 @ 11:45 am Patrick Hynes THE ORGANIZERS of the opening ceremony of the 2024 Olympic Games thought to express their \\\"inclusivity\\\" by mocking the Christian faith through a blasphemous depiction of the Last Supper featuring gaudily dressed drag queens.\", \"from\": 281, \"to\": 564, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 325, \"end\": 332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Patrick\", \"score\": 0.9999999997298801, \"rank\": 2.6695797822105723e-10, \"text\": \"Patrick\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q43115\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Patrick\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Saint_Patrick\"}, {\"begin\": 459, \"end\": 468, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999999999718057, \"rank\": 2.8414322222650673e-11, \"text\": \"Christian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"11:45 am\", \"from\": 309, \"to\": 317}, {\"ngram\": \"THE ORGANIZERS\", \"from\": 332, \"to\": 346}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 370}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 374, \"to\": 396}, {\"ngram\": \"their \\\"inclusivity\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 434}, {\"ngram\": \"a blasphemous depiction\", \"from\": 475, \"to\": 498}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 502, \"to\": 517}, {\"ngram\": \"gaudily dressed drag queens\", \"from\": 528, \"to\": 555}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The execrable display was titled, \\\"La C\\u00e8ne sur la sc\\u00e8ne sur la Seine,\\\" or \\\"The Last Supper on the stage on the Seine.\\\"\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 676, \"end\": 681, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999972715, \"rank\": 2.780176249235785e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The execrable display\", \"from\": 565, \"to\": 586}, {\"ngram\": \"La C\\u00e8ne sur\", \"from\": 600, \"to\": 611}, {\"ngram\": \"sur la Seine\", \"from\": 621, \"to\": 633}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"The Last Supper\", \"from\": 639, \"to\": 655}, {\"ngram\": \"the stage\", \"from\": 659, \"to\": 668}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For a short period of time, the organizers attempted to deny that this was their intention.\", \"from\": 685, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a short period\", \"from\": 689, \"to\": 703}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 707, \"to\": 711}, {\"ngram\": \"the organizers\", \"from\": 713, \"to\": 727}, {\"ngram\": \"their intention\", \"from\": 760, \"to\": 775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But theyquickly backpedaled, issued a duplicitous apology, and acknowledged it was \\\"inspired\\\" by the famous Da Vinci mural.\", \"from\": 777, \"to\": 900, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 885, \"end\": 893, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.556523337601291e-40, \"text\": \"Da Vinci\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leonardo_da_Vinci\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a duplicitous apology\", \"from\": 813, \"to\": 834}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier this month, as part of theNational Eucharistic Revival, 60,000 Roman Catholics attended theEucharistic Congressin Indianapolis to adore the Blessed Sacrament.\", \"from\": 902, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 973, \"end\": 988, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.9493458912760512e-16, \"text\": \"Roman Catholics\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 929}, {\"ngram\": \"theNational Eucharistic Revival\", \"from\": 933, \"to\": 964}, {\"ngram\": \"theEucharistic Congressin Indianapolis\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1036}, {\"ngram\": \"the Blessed Sacrament\", \"from\": 1046, \"to\": 1067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"How providential, then, that we have the gross display at the Olympics, seen by millions, to grant us the opportunity to articulate how important the historic event of the Last Supper was to the life of the Church, and indeed for all mankind.\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1311, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"How providential\", \"from\": 1069, \"to\": 1085}, {\"ngram\": \"the gross display\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1123}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1139}, {\"ngram\": \"millions\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1157}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1168, \"to\": 1170}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1171, \"to\": 1186}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic event\", \"from\": 1215, \"to\": 1233}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1237, \"to\": 1252}, {\"ngram\": \"the life\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1268}, {\"ngram\": \"the Church\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1282}, {\"ngram\": \"all mankind\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To start, though, I hope the Olympic organizers and their apologists understand how paltry their mockery of Jesus really was.\", \"from\": 1313, \"to\": 1438, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1421, \"end\": 1426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.393676242667708e-11, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympic organizers\", \"from\": 1338, \"to\": 1360}, {\"ngram\": \"their apologists\", \"from\": 1365, \"to\": 1381}, {\"ngram\": \"their mockery\", \"from\": 1404, \"to\": 1417}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Within hours of the Last Supper, Jesus was betrayed, arrested, beaten, tried, and crucified.\", \"from\": 1439, \"to\": 1531, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1477, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.393676242667708e-11, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hours\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1451}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1470}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sneering crowds belittled him as \\\"the king of the Jews.\\\"\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1582, \"end\": 1586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"score\": 0.9367589701919036, \"rank\": 0.06751046087697449, \"text\": \"Jews\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Judaism\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Sneering crowds\", \"from\": 1532, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"the king\", \"from\": 1566, \"to\": 1574}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His own friends abandoned Him at His most desperate hour.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1646, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His own friends\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"His most desperate hour\", \"from\": 1622, \"to\": 1645}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mockery was nothing new to Jesus and the earliest Christians.\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1708, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1674, \"end\": 1679, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.393676242667708e-11, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 1697, \"end\": 1707, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999778735229065, \"rank\": 2.2126555469567e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Mockery\", \"from\": 1647, \"to\": 1654}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 1659, \"to\": 1666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is an increasingly familiar reality to Christians today.\", \"from\": 1709, \"to\": 1768, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1751, \"end\": 1761, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"score\": 0.9999778735229065, \"rank\": 2.2126555469567e-05, \"text\": \"Christians\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Christianity\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an increasingly familiar reality\", \"from\": 1715, \"to\": 1747}]}, {\"sentence\": \"People should know what the Last Supper was all about.\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"People\", \"from\": 1770, \"to\": 1776}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1794, \"to\": 1809}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Constitution on the Sacred Liturgy of the Roman Catholic Church,Sacrosanctum Concilium, reads: \\\"At the Last Supper, on the night when He was betrayed, our Saviour instituted the eucharistic sacrifice of His Body and Blood.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 2052, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1871, \"end\": 1892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.9375670831423935e-15, \"text\": \"Roman Catholic Church\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Catholic_Church\"}, {\"begin\": 1893, \"end\": 1915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sacrosanctum_Concilium\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sacrosanctum Concilium\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sacrosanctum_Concilium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sacrosanctum_Concilium\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Constitution\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1841}, {\"ngram\": \"the Sacred Liturgy\", \"from\": 1845, \"to\": 1863}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 1943}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 1948, \"to\": 1957}, {\"ngram\": \"our Saviour\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 1991}, {\"ngram\": \"the eucharistic sacrifice\", \"from\": 2003, \"to\": 2028}, {\"ngram\": \"His Body\", \"from\": 2032, \"to\": 2040}, {\"ngram\": \"Blood\", \"from\": 2045, \"to\": 2050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He did this in order to perpetuate the sacrifice of the Cross throughout the centuries until He should come again, and so to entrust to His beloved spouse, the Church, a memorial of His death and resurrection: a sacrament of love, a sign of unity, a bond of charity, a paschal banquet in which Christ is eaten, the mind is filled with grace, and a pledge of future glory is given to us\\\" (SC 47).\", \"from\": 2053, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2068, \"to\": 2073}, {\"ngram\": \"the sacrifice\", \"from\": 2088, \"to\": 2101}, {\"ngram\": \"the Cross\", \"from\": 2105, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"the centuries\", \"from\": 2126, \"to\": 2139}, {\"ngram\": \"His beloved spouse\", \"from\": 2189, \"to\": 2207}, {\"ngram\": \"the Church\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"a memorial\", \"from\": 2221, \"to\": 2231}, {\"ngram\": \"His death\", \"from\": 2235, \"to\": 2244}, {\"ngram\": \"resurrection\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2261}, {\"ngram\": \"a sacrament\", \"from\": 2263, \"to\": 2274}, {\"ngram\": \"love\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2282}, {\"ngram\": \"a sign\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2290}, {\"ngram\": \"unity\", \"from\": 2294, \"to\": 2299}, {\"ngram\": \"a bond\", \"from\": 2301, \"to\": 2307}, {\"ngram\": \"charity\", \"from\": 2311, \"to\": 2318}, {\"ngram\": \"a paschal banquet\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2337}, {\"ngram\": \"Christ\", \"from\": 2347, \"to\": 2353}, {\"ngram\": \"the mind\", \"from\": 2364, \"to\": 2372}, {\"ngram\": \"grace\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2393}, {\"ngram\": \"a pledge\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2407}, {\"ngram\": \"future glory\", \"from\": 2411, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2436, \"to\": 2438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In other words, at the Last Supper, Jesus initiated the final stage of His public ministry.\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2541, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2486, \"end\": 2491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.393676242667708e-11, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"other words\", \"from\": 2453, \"to\": 2464}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2469, \"to\": 2484}, {\"ngram\": \"the final stage\", \"from\": 2502, \"to\": 2517}, {\"ngram\": \"His public ministry\", \"from\": 2521, \"to\": 2540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was here that Jesus instituted the Holy Eucharist, giving the Church its most powerful sacrament, the \\\"true bread from heaven,\\\" (John 6:32) his flesh.\", \"from\": 2542, \"to\": 2695, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2559, \"end\": 2564, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.393676242667708e-11, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}, {\"begin\": 2580, \"end\": 2594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.470872117454664e-42, \"text\": \"Holy Eucharist\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eucharist\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Church\", \"from\": 2603, \"to\": 2613}, {\"ngram\": \"its most powerful sacrament\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2641}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"true bread\", \"from\": 2643, \"to\": 2658}, {\"ngram\": \"heaven\", \"from\": 2664, \"to\": 2670}, {\"ngram\": \"John\", \"from\": 2674, \"to\": 2678}, {\"ngram\": \"his flesh\", \"from\": 2685, \"to\": 2694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I am the living bread that came down from heaven; whoever eats this bread will live forever; and the bread that I will give is my flesh for the life of the world,\\\" Jesus told a skeptical crowd (John 6:51).\", \"from\": 2697, \"to\": 2903, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2862, \"end\": 2867, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.393676242667708e-11, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the living bread\", \"from\": 2703, \"to\": 2719}, {\"ngram\": \"heaven\", \"from\": 2740, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"whoever\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2755}, {\"ngram\": \"this bread\", \"from\": 2761, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"the bread\", \"from\": 2795, \"to\": 2804}, {\"ngram\": \"my flesh\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"the life\", \"from\": 2838, \"to\": 2846}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 2859}, {\"ngram\": \"a skeptical crowd\", \"from\": 2873, \"to\": 2890}, {\"ngram\": \"John\", \"from\": 2892, \"to\": 2896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He gave us this bread at the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 2904, \"to\": 2945, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2914}, {\"ngram\": \"this bread\", \"from\": 2915, \"to\": 2925}, {\"ngram\": \"the Last Supper\", \"from\": 2929, \"to\": 2944}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Shortly thereafter he would die on a cross in fulfillment of ancient scriptures, making eternal life available to all.\", \"from\": 2946, \"to\": 3064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a cross\", \"from\": 2981, \"to\": 2988}, {\"ngram\": \"fulfillment\", \"from\": 2992, \"to\": 3003}, {\"ngram\": \"ancient scriptures\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3025}, {\"ngram\": \"eternal life\", \"from\": 3034, \"to\": 3046}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"No one has greater love than this, to lay down one's life for one's friends\\\" (John 15:13).\", \"from\": 3066, \"to\": 3157, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No one\", \"from\": 3067, \"to\": 3073}, {\"ngram\": \"greater love\", \"from\": 3078, \"to\": 3090}, {\"ngram\": \"one's life\", \"from\": 3114, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"one's friends\", \"from\": 3129, \"to\": 3142}, {\"ngram\": \"John\", \"from\": 3145, \"to\": 3149}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You want inclusivity?\", \"from\": 3159, \"to\": 3180, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"inclusivity\", \"from\": 3168, \"to\": 3179}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every human being has access to eternal life through the sacrifice Jesus initiated at the Last Supper.\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3248, \"end\": 3253, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"score\": 0.9999999999463398, \"rank\": 5.393676242667708e-11, \"text\": \"Jesus\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jesus\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Every human being\", \"from\": 3181, \"to\": 3198}, {\"ngram\": \"access\", \"from\": 3203, \"to\": 3209}